# Repo-root allowlist.
#
# This directory (9EconTools) is the working tree of the `econtools` git repo,
# but it ALSO physically holds many unrelated workspace folders and loose files
# (other projects, screenshots, PDFs, exports). To stop a stray `git add -A`
# from sweeping those into the repo, we ignore EVERYTHING at the top level and
# then re-include only the folders/files this repo actually tracks.
#
# Adding a new top-level project to this repo? Add a matching `!/<name>/` line.

/*

!/.gitignore
!/README.md
!/.claude-plugin/
!/diebolt/
!/ehrstyle/
!/janluiten/
!/kabbo/
!/kris/
!/tanniedi/
!/tyler/
